{"tid":915435,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[白皮豬] 見到黑人就開槍？ 警將非裔美軍誤當槍手射殺","createTime":"2018-11-25T03:49:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-25T07:39:50.000Z","uid":64191,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"1cbade659e0924a0e1a84f39632f9f5ae236f4b8","tid":915435,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T03:49:55.000Z","msg":"警方表示，周四晚間一名男子在伯明罕（Birmingham）市郊的瑞佛切斯拱廊（RiverchaseGalleria）購物中心2樓大廳與一名18歲青年發生推撞，男子突然向對方連開2槍。兩名駐警聽到槍聲後趕到現場，碰巧目睹到手持槍枝的死者，隨即開槍將他擊斃。整個過程中，另有一名12歲女孩被流彈所傷，但情況穩定。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事件後，警方一度聲稱，已擊斃槍手，但周六（24日）突然改口，坦承殺錯人。胡佛市（Hoover）警局說，新證據顯示，21歲的男性死者布拉德福德（Emantic Fitzgerald BradfordJr.）是美軍的戰鬥工程師，雖然他可能涉入周四晚間的爭執（在現場口角的多於兩人），但開槍傷人的並不是他，他只是在逃跑時揮動手槍，才被擊斃。目前開槍的員警已被停職，警方仍在追捕真正的槍手。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/ncmTLk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FncmTLk&d=HyPHtKP0X271k9gPNCCtZ7ZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=4c37d0af\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/ncmTLk</a>"},{"pid":"40be6068b543c3fb985d68e4689ffa303cffdf85","tid":915435,"uid":179967,"like":75,"dislike":0,"score":75,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T03:53:28.000Z","msg":"根本racist係外國根深柢固<br />\n推崇無分種族根本無可能"},{"pid":"66312c9c572d6713844de653033a2baea821aa7b","tid":915435,"uid":97078,"like":29,"dislike":14,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T03:59:29.000Z","msg":"碰巧目睹到手持槍枝的死者，隨即開槍將他擊斃<br />\n<br />\n可能我中文差 個死者死左 手持槍枝 再比警察鞭屍?"},{"pid":"2c3cd5572ea9d52864c4dd6ff0050cbc34132b03","tid":915435,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T03:59:46.000Z","msg":"黑人rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ff3d27b7ca1eecca6ceef4677f1526d662d84e0","tid":915435,"uid":47470,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"66312c9c572d6713844de653033a2baea821aa7b","tid":915435,"uid":97078,"like":29,"dislike":14,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T03:59:29.000Z","msg":"碰巧目睹到手持槍枝的死者，隨即開槍將他擊斃<br />\n<br />\n可能我中文差 個死者死左 手持槍枝 再比警察鞭屍?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T04:01:17.000Z","msg":"又真係咁差都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a200fc3d93db624fa73d8e103636c927aa44075","tid":915435,"uid":179967,"like":25,"dislike":4,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T04:02:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>碰巧目睹到手持槍枝的死者，隨即開槍將他擊斃<br />\n<br />\n可能我中文差 個死者死左 手持槍枝 再比警察鞭屍?</blockquote><br />\n俾警察殺左咪死者<br />\n你個腦呢?"},{"pid":"c2dcc26dfa01f722f080416800f5ad64c37eaa6a","tid":915435,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":44,"score":-42,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T04:02:18.000Z","msg":"人地錯左, 起碼會認錯, 同埋係美國呢D賠償係天文數字<br />\n<br />\n香港？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1429916-20181124.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1429916-20181124.htm&d=HyPHtKP0X271k9gPNCCtZ7ZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=1465ef43\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1429916-20181124.htm&h=413329c0\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1429916-20181124.htm</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>盧偉聰：女警開槍決定正確　疑犯家屬指控不公道</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1429938_1_L_20181124184558.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1429938_1_L_20181124184558.jpg&h=2d178d3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警務處處長盧偉聰表示，深水埗港鐵站今個月7日發生的警員開槍案，警方已找到5名目擊者，另外翻看了案發現場附近的閉路電視錄影片段，警方初步調查，確認當日警員向涉嫌襲警的男子開槍是正確決定，他又說當時電光火石之間，警員選擇開槍是為了保護自己和市民安全，如當時女警選擇閃避，可能會受嚴重傷害，疑犯有可能在站內傷害市民，特別是當時有很多學生準備上學。<br />\n<br />\n被問到疑犯家屬早前召開記者會，指警方無向他們交代調查進度，在事發後又無進行問卷調查，找尋目擊者。盧偉聰回應說，有關指控不公道，因警方一般會在無法找到目擊者，又無閉路電視錄像的情況下，才做問卷調查，另外今次案件涉及刑事調查，警方至今未能與疑犯錄口供，在未完成調查前無可能作交代，他說明白家屬的感受，又指將來所有證據及細節，會在法庭上披露。<br />\n<br />\n盧偉聰表示，警隊是高效而專業，調查不會「嘆慢板」，而警員是受過嚴格訓練，警員開槍給予自己的麻煩會好多，但仍做出相關決定，希望市民諒解，並以有這樣一位肯承擔，做勇敢決定的警員為榮。"},{"pid":"94d5ea9a1b68a1c7dcd483e734582b0c2581c96b","tid":915435,"uid":32722,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T04:02:29.000Z","msg":"如果係香港我都射鳩蝻先，寧願放生個mk仔"},{"pid":"ac7e834cc871464e18a501ce6ba15ae25b468b39","tid":915435,"uid":18735,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2a200fc3d93db624fa73d8e103636c927aa44075","tid":915435,"uid":179967,"like":25,"dislike":4,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T04:02:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>碰巧目睹到手持槍枝的死者，隨即開槍將他擊斃<br />\n<br />\n可能我中文差 個死者死左 手持槍枝 再比警察鞭屍?</blockquote><br />\n俾警察殺左咪死者<br />\n你個腦呢?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T04:04:51.000Z","msg":"篇文真係寫得差喎"},{"pid":"99fcce6a385a55f4af5b2f7b27228257e98ccdde","tid":915435,"uid":143499,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"c2dcc26dfa01f722f080416800f5ad64c37eaa6a","tid":915435,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":44,"score":-42,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T04:02:18.000Z","msg":"人地錯左, 起碼會認錯, 同埋係美國呢D賠償係天文數字<br />\n<br />\n香港？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1429916-20181124.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1429916-20181124.htm&d=HyPHtKP0X271k9gPNCCtZ7ZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=1465ef43\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1429916-20181124.htm&h=413329c0\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1429916-20181124.htm</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>盧偉聰：女警開槍決定正確　疑犯家屬指控不公道</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1429938_1_L_20181124184558